Interface Attribute

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AttributeDesignator, SAMLObject, org.opensaml.core.xml.XMLObject

    public interface Attribute
extends AttributeDesignator
    This interface defines how the object representing a SAML 1 Attribute element behaves.
